window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>In a realm where alliances are forged through royal decrees, Cassia, the proud daughter of Nimuria, finds her fate abruptly altered by a proclamation of unity. Torn from the familiar shores of her homeland, she is destined to wed Louie, the future king of Allagash, Nimuria's long-standing adversary. As she navigates the treacherous waters of an impending political marriage, Cassia discovers hidden layers of intrigue, encountering rumors of magic, familial secrets, whispers of war, and the enigmatic Agenor. Forced into a world of uncertainty, Cassia must wield not only her sword but also her wits as she unravels the threads of a destiny interwoven with ancient rivalries, submerged truths, and the timeless struggle between the mortal and divine. Unveil the intricate tapestry of a world teetering between magic and reality, where alliances shift like shadows and the truest hearts are tested. In this epic saga of love, loss, and self-discovery, every choice echoes through the corridors of fate, leaving an indelible mark on the destinies of gods and men alike.</p>"; 
